msgid "The silhouette of a large clock is reflected here."
msgstr "大きな時計のシルエットが映っている。"

msgid "A large window shaped like a clock towers above you."
msgstr "時計のような形の大きな窓が上にそびえている。"

msgid "The time is set to 12:00."
msgstr "時刻は12時だ。"

msgid "There you are!"
msgstr "あ、いた！"

msgid "How'd you get in there?"
msgstr "どうやって入ったんだ？"

msgid "I got zapped, like there's something keeping me out."
msgstr "俺は何かに阻まれたみたいにバチッてなったぜ。"

msgid "Really?"
msgstr "ほんとに？"

msgid "You didn't even notice me gone!?"
msgstr "俺がいないのも気付かなかったのか!?"

msgid "...."
msgstr "……"

msgid "No."
msgstr "うん。"

msgid "Cold..."
msgstr "冷たいな……"

msgid "So what was in there anyway?"
msgstr "で、中には何があったんだ？"

msgid "Anything fun?"
msgstr "楽しいものか？"

msgid "Yes, very fun."
msgstr "うん、すごく楽しかった。"

msgid "What? Really??"
msgstr "何？　マジか??"

msgid "What was it?"
msgstr "何があったんだ？"

msgid "I can't tell you."
msgstr "言えない。"

msgid "Huh?!"
msgstr "はぁ!?"

msgid "Why not??"
msgstr "何でだよ??"

msgid "Because it's more fun that way."
msgstr "そのほうがもっと楽しいから。"

msgid "No way, don't do me dirty like this!"
msgstr "おい、意地悪はやめろよ！"

msgid "..."
msgstr "……"

msgid "(It's strange though. Why wasn't he able to enter?)"
msgstr "(でも不思議。どうしてサイは入れなかったんだろう？)"
